cu.explanation_en: Setting the second integrity algorithm to the unknown enum 'nia9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the maximum MIMO layers to an out-of-range value of 99 will cause configuration validation failure during initialization.
du.explanation_zh: 將最大 MIMO 層數設定為超出範圍的值 99 會在初始化期間導致配置驗證失敗。
